
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../stylesheets/uploadform.css">
  <title><%= data.review.reviewTitle %></title>
</head>
    <body class="upload-form-body">
        <a class="back-btn" href='/review_overview'>Terug naar overzicht</a>
       <main>
        <form id="review-form" action="/review/<%=data._id%>" method="post" autocomplete="on">
        <h1><%= data.review.reviewTitle %></h1>
          <section>
            <h2>Over de recensent</h2>
            <label>
              <p>Je naam:</p>
              <input type="text" name="name" required value="<%= data.user.name %>">
            </label>

            <label>
              <p>Je email:</p>
              <input type="email" name="email" required value="<%= data.user.email %>">
            </label>

            <label>
              <p>Datum</p>
              <input type="date" name="postDate" required value="<%= data.user.postDate %>">
            </label>

          </section>

          <section>
            <h2>Serie meta informatie</h2>

            <label>
              <p>Titel:</p>
              <p class="sub-line">Zorg ervoor dat de titel uniek is. Wanneer een serie twee verschillende titels heeft. Gebruik dan de meest frequent gebruikte titel.</p>
              <input type="text" name="seriesName" required value="<%= data.review.seriesName %>">
            </label>

            <label>
              <p>Land van herkomst:</p>
              <p class="sub-line">Gebruik de internationale landcodes. Zorg ervoor dat ze allemaal in hoofdletters zijn, zodat er altijd overeenkomsten zijn.</p>
              <input type="text" name="regionCode" value="<%= data.review.region %>" required>
            </label>

            <label>
              <p>Beginjaar:</p>
              <p class="sub-line">Het jaartal waarin de serie begon met opnemen.</p>
              <input type="text" name="startingYear" value="<%= data.review.startYear %>" required>
            </label>

            <label>
              <p>Eindjaar:</p>
              <p class="sub-line">Draait de serie nog steeds? Zet dan ‘heden’ in het veld.</p>
              <input type="text" name="endYear" value="<%= data.review.endYear %>" required>
            </label>

            <div>
              <h3>Categorie:</h3>
              <p class="sub-line">Vink de genres aan waarbin deze serie hoort.</p>
              <label>
                  <input type="checkbox"
                      <% if (data.review.genre.includes('action')) { %>
                          checked
                      <% } %>
                  name="genre" value="action">
                  <span>Actie</span>
              </label>
              <label>
                  <input type="checkbox"
                  <% if (data.review.genre.includes('adventure')) { %>
                      checked
                  <% } %>
                  name="genre" value="adventure">
                  <span>Avontuur</span>
              </label>

              <label>
                  <input type="checkbox"
                  <% if (data.review.genre.includes('comedy')) { %>
                      checked
                  <% } %>
                  name="genre" value="comedy">
                  <span>Comedy</span>
              </label>

              <label>
                  <input type="checkbox"
                  <% if (data.review.genre.includes('documentary')) { %>
                      checked
                  <% } %>
                   name="genre" value="documentary">
                  <span>Documentaire</span>
              </label>

              <label>
                  <input type="checkbox"
                  <% if (data.review.genre.includes('drama')) { %>
                      checked
                  <% } %>
                 name="genre" value="drama">
                  <span>Drama</span>
              </label>

              <label>
                  <input type="checkbox"
                  <% if (data.review.genre.includes('epic')) { %>
                      checked
                  <% } %>
                  name="genre" value="epic">
                  <span>Episch
              </label>

              <label>
                  <input type="checkbox"
                  <% if (data.review.genre.includes('horror')) { %>
                      checked
                  <% } %>
                  name="genre" value="horror">
                  <span>Horror</span>
              </label>

              <label>
                  <input type="checkbox"
                  <% if (data.review.genre.includes('scifi')) { %>
                      checked
                  <% } %>
                  name="genre" value="scifi">
                  <span>Sci-fi</span>
              </label>

              <label>
                  <input type="checkbox"
                  <% if (data.review.genre.includes('war')) { %>
                      checked
                  <% } %>
                  name="genre" value="war">
                  <span>Oorlog</span>
              </label>

              <label>
                  <input type="checkbox"
                  <% if (data.review.genre.includes('romance')) { %>
                      checked
                  <% } %>
                  name="genre" value="romance">
                  <span>Romantiek</span>
              </label>

              <label>
                  <input type="checkbox"
                  <% if (data.review.genre.includes('music')) { %>
                      checked
                  <% } %>
                  name="genre" value="music">
                  <span>Muziek</span>
              </label>

              <label>
                  <input type="checkbox"
                  <% if (data.review.genre.includes('fantasy')) { %>
                      checked
                  <% } %>
                  name="genre" value="fantasy">
                  <span>Fantasy</span>
              </label>

              <label>
                  <input type="checkbox"
                  <% if (data.review.genre.includes('thriller')) { %>
                      checked
                  <% } %>
                  name="genre" value="thriller">
                  <span>Thriller</span>
              </label>

              <label>
                  <input type="checkbox"
                  <% if (data.review.genre.includes('crime')) { %>
                      checked
                  <% } %>
                  name="genre" value="crime">
                  <span>Misdaad</span>
              </label>

              <label>
                  <input type="checkbox"
                  <% if (data.review.genre.includes('sport')) { %>
                      checked
                  <% } %>
                  name="genre" value="sport">
                  <span>Sport</span>
              </label>

              <label>
                  <input type="checkbox"
                  <% if (data.review.genre.includes('mystery')) { %>
                      checked
                  <% } %>
                  name="genre" value="mystery">
                  <span>Mystery</span>
              </label>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3>Beschikbaarheid</h3>
              <p class="sub-line">Op welk platform kan de serie bekeken worden?</p>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.platform.includes('netflix')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="platform" value="netflix">
                <span>Netflix</span>
              </label>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.platform.includes('hbo')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="platform" value="hbo">
                <span>HBO</span>
              </label>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.platform.includes('videoland')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="platform" value="videoland">
                <span>Videoland</span>
              </label>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.platform.includes('disc')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="platform" value="disc">
                <span>DVD/Bluray</span>
              </label>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3>Tijdperk</h3>
              <p class="sub-line">In welke tijd speelt het verhaal zich af?</p>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.period.includes('prehistoric')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="period" value="prehistoric">
                <span>Prehistorie</span>

              </label>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.period.includes('roman')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="period" value="roman">
                <span>Romeinse Tijd</span>

              </label>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.period.includes('middleages')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="period" value="middleages">
                <span>Middeleeuwen</span>

              </label>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.period.includes('victorian')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="period" value="victorian">
                <span>Victoriaanse Tijd</span>

              </label>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.period.includes('wo1')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="period" value="wo1">
                <span>Eerste Wereldoorlog</span>

              </label>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.period.includes('wo2')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="period" value="wo2">
                <span>Tweede Wereldoorlog</span>

              </label>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.period.includes('late20')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="period" value="late20">
                <span>Late 20e Eeuw</span>

              </label>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.period.includes('present')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="period" value="present">
                <span>Heden</span>

              </label>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.period.includes('future')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="period" value="future">
                <span>Toekomst</span>

              </label>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3>Passende Persona's</h3>
              <p>Welke persona's passen het beste bij deze serie?</p>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.persona.includes('foodie')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="persona" value="foodie">
                <span>Foodie</span>

              </label>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.persona.includes('creative')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="persona" value="creative">
                <span>Creatieveling</span>

              </label>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.persona.includes('sensationalist')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="persona" value="sensationalist">
                <span>Sensatiezoeker</span>

              </label>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.persona.includes('joker')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="persona" value="joker">
                <span>Grappenmaker</span>

              </label>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.persona.includes('girly')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="persona" value="girly">
                <span>Girly Girl</span>

              </label>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.persona.includes('tomboy')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="persona" value="tomboy">
                <span>Tomboy</span>

              </label>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.persona.includes('daredevil')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="persona" value="daredevil">
                <span>Waaghals</span>

              </label>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.persona.includes('adventurer')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="persona" value="adventurer">
                <span>Avonturier</span>

              </label>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.persona.includes('nerd')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="persona" value="nerd">
                <span>Geeky Nerd</span>

              </label>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.persona.includes('animallover')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="persona" value="animallover">
                <span>Dierenliefhebber</span>

              </label>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.persona.includes('intellectual')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="persona" value="intellectual">
                <span>Intellectueell</span>

              </label>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3>Passende Hobby's</h3>
              <p class="sub-line">Welke hobby's passen het beste bij deze serie?</p>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.hobby.includes('gaming')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="hobby" value="gaming">
                <span>Gamen</span>

              </label>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.hobby.includes('party')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="hobby" value="party">
                <span>Uitgaan/borrelen</span>

              </label>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.hobby.includes('travel')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="hobby" value="travel">
                <span>Reizen</span>

              </label>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.hobby.includes('music')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="hobby" value="music">
                <span>Muziek</span>

              </label>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.hobby.includes('shopping')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="hobby" value="shopping">
                <span>Shoppen</span>

              </label>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.hobby.includes('cooking')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="hobby" value="cooking">
                <span>Koken</span>

              </label>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.hobby.includes('sport')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="hobby" value="sport">
                <span>Sporten</span>

              </label>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.hobby.includes('reading')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="hobby" value="reading">
                <span>Lezen</span>

              </label>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.hobby.includes('drugs')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="hobby" value="drugs">
                <span>Drugs</span>

              </label>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.hobby.includes('working')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="hobby" value="working">
                <span>Werken</span>

              </label>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3>Passende Moods</h3>
              <p class="sub-line">Welke moods passen het beste bij deze serie?</p>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.mood.includes('scared')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="mood" value="scared">
                <span>Ik wil bang gemaakt worden</span>

              </label>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.mood.includes('cry')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="mood" value="cry">
                <span>Ik wil lekker janken</span>

              </label>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.mood.includes('thrill')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="mood" value="thrill">
                <span>Ik wil van spanning stoppen met ademen</span>

              </label>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.mood.includes('laugh')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="mood" value="laugh">
                <span>Ik wil huilen van het lachen</span>

              </label>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.mood.includes('chill')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="mood" value="chill">
                <span>Ik wil hersendood voor de TV zitten</span>

              </label>
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox"
                <% if (data.review.mood.includes('learn')) { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                name="mood" value="learn">
                <span>Ik wil iets leren</span>

              </label>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3>Leeftijdsclassificatie</h3>
              <label>
                <p class="sub-line">Vanaf welke leeftijd mag de serie bekeken worden?</p>
                <input type="text" name="ageRestriction" value="<%= data.review.ageRestriction %>" required>
              </label>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3>Seizoenen</h3>
              <label>
                <span>Aantal:</span>
                <input type="text" name="seasons" value="<%= data.review.seasons %>" required>
              </label>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3>Afleveringen</h3>
              <label>
                <span>Totaal Aantal:</span>
                <input type="text" name="episodes" value="<%= data.review.episodes %>" required>
              </label>
              <label>
                <span>Duur Per Aflevering:</span>
                <input type="text" name="duration" value="<%= data.review.duration %>" required>
              </label>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3>Cast</h3>
              <label>
                <span>Hoofdacteurs/actrices (maximaal 6, scheiden met komma)</span>
                <input type="text" name="actors" value="<%= data.review.actors %>" required>
              </label>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3>Regie</h3>
              <label>
                <span>Regie (maximaal 2, scheiden met komma)</span>
                <input type="text" name="producers" value="<%= data.review.producers %>" required>
              </label>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3>IMDB rating</h3>
              <label>
                <span>Wat is de IMDB beoordeling?</span>
                <input type="text" name="imdbRating" value="<%= data.review.imdbRating %>" required>
              </label>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3>Trailer</h3>
              <p class="sub-line">Plaats hier de <em>Embed URL</em> (dus niet de reguliere link) naar de trailer op YouTube. Geen trailer? Laat het veld dan leeg.</p>
              <label>
                <span>Link naar de trailer</span>
                <input type="text" name="trailerURL" value="<%= data.review.trailerURL %>" placeholder="Bijv. https://www.youtube.com/embed/v7MGUNV8MxU">
              </label>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3>Afbeelding</h3>
              <p class="sub-line">Plaats hier de URL naar de poster van de serie, in portret modus.</p>
              <label>
                <span>Link naar afbeelding</span>
                <input type="text" name="imgURL" value="<%= data.review.imgURL %>" required>
              </label>
            </div>


          </section>
          <section>
            <h2>Recensie</h2>

            <label>
              <h3>Titel</h3>
              <input type="text" name="reviewTitle" value="<%= data.review.reviewTitle %>">
            </label>

            <label>
              <h3>Plot:</h3>
              <p class="sub-line">Korte omschrijving van de serie (voor op de website):</p>
              <textarea name="reviewPlot" rows="8" cols="80" required><%= data.review.reviewPlot %></textarea>
            </label>

            <label>
              <h3>Inleiding:</h3>
              <textarea name="reviewIntro" rows="8" cols="80"><%= data.review.reviewIntro %></textarea>
            </label>

            <label>
              <h3>Recensie:</h3>
              <textarea name="reviewBody" rows="8" cols="80"><%= data.review.reviewBody %></textarea>
            </label>

            <label>
              Welk cijfer geef je aan deze serie? (1 t/m 10): <br>
                <input type="text" name="reviewRating" required value="<%= data.review.reviewRating %>">
            </label>
          </section>

          <input class="upload-btn" type="submit" value="Bijwerken">
        </form>
    </main>

</body>
</html>
